```
LOOP:
  1. Tell user to open http://localhost:PORT/finalized.html (or open file directly)

  2. If approved mockup PNG exists, show inline (Read tool) for comparison.
     Skip if plan-driven or freeform mode.

  3. AskUserQuestion:
